        'SANDRO cannot be held responsible for any delay in delivery due entirely to the unavailability of the Customer following several attempts by the carrier to arrange for delivery.' => 'SANDRO cannot be held responsible for any delay in delivery due entirely to the unavailability of the Customer following several attempts by the carrier to arrange for delivery.',
